<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Women's Safety Tips</title>
  <style>/* Reset */
    * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }
      
      /* Body and Base Styles */
      body {
        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        background-color: #f0f2f5;
        color: #333;
        line-height: 1.6;
        background-image: url('image/background.jpg'); /* Replace with the actual path of your image */
        background-size: cover; /* Ensures the image covers the whole page */
        background-repeat: no-repeat; /* Prevents the image from repeating */
        background-position: center; /* Centers the image */
        background-attachment: fixed; /* Keeps the background image fixed while scrolling */
        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; /* Ensures text remains visible */
      }
      
      /* Header */
      header {
        background-color: #FF4C5B; /* Accent color for your app */
        padding: 15px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      
      header nav ul {
        list-style: none;
        margin: 0;
      }
      
      header nav ul li {
        display: inline;
        margin-right: 20px;
      }
      
      header nav ul li a {
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        padding: 5px 10px;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      }
      
      header nav ul li a:hover {
        background-color: #ff7c85;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
      
      /* Safety Tips Section */
      #safety-tips-section {
        padding: 40px 0;
        background-color: #fff;
      }
      
      .container {
        width: 90%;
        margin: 0 auto;
        max-width: 1200px;
      }
      
      h2 {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
        color: #FF4C5B; /* Matches header color */
        font-size: 2.2rem;
      }
      
      .tips-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 30px;
      }
      
      /* Tip Cards */
      .tip-card {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
      }
      
      .tip-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-10px);
      }
      
      .tip-card img {
        width: 50px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      
      .tip-card h3 {
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        font-size: 1.3rem;
      }
      
      .tip-card p {
        color: #555;
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.4;
      }
      
      /* Responsive */
      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .tips-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
      }
      </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Header Section -->
  <header>
    <div class="navbar">
      <h1>Women Safety App</h1>
      <nav>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/">Home</a></li> <!-- Update links to match routes -->
          <li><a href="/safety-tips">Safety Tips & Modules</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Safety Tips Section -->
  <section id="safety-tips-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Women's Safety Tips & Modules</h2>
      
      <div class="tips-grid">

        <!-- Tip Card 1 -->
        <div class="tip-card">
          <img src="https://img.icons8.com/fluent/48/000000/location.png" alt="Share Location">
          <h3>Tip 1: Share Your Location</h3>
          <p>Always share your live location with trusted contacts when traveling alone, especially at night.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Tip Card 2 -->
        <div class="tip-card">
          <img src="https://img.icons8.com/fluent/48/000000/phone.png" alt="Emergency Contacts">
          <h3>Tip 2: Keep Emergency Contacts Ready</h3>
          <p>Have a list of emergency contacts saved for quick access. Many smartphones allow setting them on the lock screen.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Tip Card 3 -->
        <div class="tip-card">
          <img src="https://img.icons8.com/fluent/48/000000/self-defense.png" alt="Self-defense">
          <h3>Module: Self-defense Techniques</h3>
          <p>Learn basic self-defense techniques to protect yourself. Many online resources and courses are available for training.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Tip Card 4 -->
        <div class="tip-card">
          <img src="https://img.icons8.com/fluent/48/000000/warning-shield.png" alt="Awareness">
          <h3>Tip 3: Be Aware of Your Surroundings</h3>
          <p>Stay alert, especially in unfamiliar areas. Avoid distractions like using your phone while walking in public.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</body>
</html>
